{
  "id": "RAW_e432b38b",
  "title": "State of AI 2025：OpenRouter 真实世界 LLM 使用情况报告-百万亿级 Token 实证研究英中对照版.PDF",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650450460&idx=1&sn=b9538107b6135bcafb5dc18e9518eec0",
  "date": "2025-12-07 03:59:00",
  "author": "AINLP",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\"><span textstyle=\"\">《State of AI》是由&nbsp;</span></span><em data-start=\"217\" data-end=\"229\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">OpenRouter</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;基于过去一年用户在平台上真实调用超过&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"249\" data-end=\"266\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">100 万亿 tokens</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\"><span textstyle=\"\">&nbsp;的数据所做的首次大规模“AI 实际使用模式”统计研究。报告试图回答一个核心问题：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"351\"><strong data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"351\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人们真正如何使用大语言模型？哪些模型、任务类型与行为占据真实世界的主流？</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"353\" data-end=\"396\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这与学界 benchmark 的测试方法不同，它反映了 AI 在真实世界中的演化方向。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"403\" data-end=\"438\"><strong data-start=\"406\" data-end=\"438\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1. AI 使用分布：角色扮演、创意生成与代码任务占主导</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"440\" data-end=\"475\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报告显示，AI 的真实使用分布与传统想象中“写作”、“问答”大为不同：</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"477\" data-end=\"507\"><strong data-start=\"481\" data-end=\"507\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开源模型：以“聊天、角色扮演、创意输出”为主</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"510\" data-end=\"536\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">超过&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"513\" data-end=\"532\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">50% 的开源模型 Token</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;用于：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"555\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">角色扮演（roleplay）</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p data-start=\"560\" data-end=\"564\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">长篇对话</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p data-start=\"569\" data-end=\"577\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">创意内容生成</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"580\" data-end=\"632\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些任务通常偏娱乐性、互动性，用户追求自由度与个性化，因而更偏好无需严格政策约束且调教更灵活的开源模型。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h3 data-start=\"634\" data-end=\"662\"><strong data-start=\"638\" data-end=\"662\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">闭源 / 商用模型：以“代码与推理”为主</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"665\" data-end=\"699\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在顶级商用模型（GPT-4.1 / o3 / Claude 等）中：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p data-start=\"704\" data-end=\"722\"><strong data-start=\"704\" data-end=\"715\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">代码生成与调试</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;占据主要流量</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p data-start=\"727\" data-end=\"769\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">各类 reasoning（推理、任务规划、workflow 执行）使用量持续增长</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"772\" data-end=\"795\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说明商业环境更重视精确性、可靠性与强推理能力。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"797\" data-end=\"802\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">结论：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"805\" data-end=\"842\"><strong data-start=\"805\" data-end=\"842\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开源模型更像“陪伴与创作工具”，闭源模型更像“生产力与工程工具”。</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h2 data-start=\"849\" data-end=\"879\"><strong data-start=\"852\" data-end=\"879\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2. Reasoning 模型正在成为主导力量</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"891\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报告中特别强调：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"894\" data-end=\"946\"><strong data-start=\"894\" data-end=\"946\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Reasoning-oriented models 现已处理超过 50% 以上的总 token。</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"948\" data-end=\"958\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这代表一种重要趋势：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"962\" data-end=\"1004\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">人类不再只要求 LLM 输出文本，而是要求它执行任务、规划步骤、调用工具、做出决策。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1039\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型正在从“文本生成器”向“推理与动作代理（agent）”转换。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1041\" data-end=\"1085\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这也解释了为什么 2024–2025 出现大量专门强化 reasoning 的模型，如：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1088\" data-end=\"1109\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OpenAI o3-mini / o3</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1125\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">DeepSeek-R1</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1128\" data-end=\"1154\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Anthropic Claude 3.7 思考版</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1157\" data-end=\"1182\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Meta Llama 4 reasoning 版本</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1184\" data-end=\"1196\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真实世界的数据证明：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"1199\" data-end=\"1222\"><strong data-start=\"1199\" data-end=\"1222\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">推理是 LLM 下一阶段的核心竞争点。</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1258\"><strong data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1258\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3. 开源模型的崛起：使用量与参与度大幅提升</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1260\" data-end=\"1282\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报告通过多个图表展示了一个持续突破性的趋势：</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1284\" data-end=\"1303\"><strong data-start=\"1288\" data-end=\"1303\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开源模型使用量增长迅猛</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1306\" data-end=\"1359\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Llama、Mistral、Qwen、DeepSeek 在 OpenRouter 上的使用量全部大幅增长。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1362\" data-end=\"1395\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在某些区域（特别是亚洲与中国市场），开源模型占比甚至领先闭源模型。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1397\" data-end=\"1402\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">原因包括：</span></span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1407\" data-end=\"1419\"><strong data-start=\"1407\" data-end=\"1417\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">成本大幅降低</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1445\"><strong data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1432\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可本地部署</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，满足隐私与灵活性需求</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1449\" data-end=\"1479\"><strong data-start=\"1449\" data-end=\"1459\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可定制化 强</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">（角色扮演、同人创作等任务特别依赖）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1483\" data-end=\"1525\"><strong data-start=\"1483\" data-end=\"1493\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">质量快速提升</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">（尤其是 DeepSeek、Qwen、Llama 4 等新模型）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p data-start=\"1527\" data-end=\"1534\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报告认为：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"1537\" data-end=\"1563\"><strong data-start=\"1537\" data-end=\"1563\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开源模型正从“补充”转变为“生态基础设施”。</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1570\" data-end=\"1616\"><strong data-start=\"1573\" data-end=\"1616\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">4. Agentic Inference：AI 使用模式从即时生成转向多步执行</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1618\" data-end=\"1630\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去 AI 使用主要是：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1632\" data-end=\"1650\"><strong data-start=\"1632\" data-end=\"1650\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">单 prompt → 单输出</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1652\" data-end=\"1656\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但如今：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1658\" data-end=\"1696\"><strong data-start=\"1658\" data-end=\"1696\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">prompt → 推理 → 工具调用 → 决策 → 再行动 → 输出</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1698\" data-end=\"1751\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报告称这种模式为&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"1707\" data-end=\"1735\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Agentic Inference（代理式推理）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，并指出这是最重要的新趋势之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1753\" data-end=\"1758\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">图表显示：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1762\" data-end=\"1789\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">带有“多阶段推理”、“调用外部工具”的任务增长显著</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1792\" data-end=\"1820\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Reasoning 模型的使用增速远高于普通对话模型</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1823\" data-end=\"1850\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">用户越来越依赖模型作为流程的一部分，而不是一个回答工具</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1852\" data-end=\"1878\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这意味着未来 AI 产品的核心不只是模型本身，而是：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"1882\" data-end=\"1919\"><strong data-start=\"1882\" data-end=\"1919\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型 + 工具 + 工作流 + 控制（orchestration）</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1926\" data-end=\"1947\"><strong data-start=\"1929\" data-end=\"1947\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">5. 多模型混合使用成为常态</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1949\" data-end=\"1958\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">用户越来越倾向于：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1962\" data-end=\"1979\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对话／角色扮演 → 选开源模型</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1982\" data-end=\"2002\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">写代码 / 推理任务 → 选闭源模型</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2005\" data-end=\"2021\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">成本敏感任务 → 选轻量模型</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2024\" data-end=\"2048\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">高精度任务 → 选顶级 reasoning 模型</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"2050\" data-end=\"2062\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报告显示用户的行为模式：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"2066\" data-end=\"2125\"><strong data-start=\"2066\" data-end=\"2101\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">No single model fits all tasks.</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个应用中频繁切换模型的情况日益普遍。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"2127\" data-end=\"2192\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这会推动未来 AI 系统发展成“模型路由器（model router）”＋“多模型代理（multi-agent system）”。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"2199\" data-end=\"2229\"><strong data-start=\"2202\" data-end=\"2229\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">6. Benchmark 与现实使用的巨大偏差</span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"2231\" data-end=\"2242\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">报告花了大量篇幅强调：</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"2244\" data-end=\"2275\"><strong data-start=\"2248\" data-end=\"2275\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">学术 benchmark 并不能反映现实需求。</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"2277\" data-end=\"2280\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">例如：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2284\" data-end=\"2316\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现实中角色扮演占据巨量流量，但 benchmark 完全忽略</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2319\" data-end=\"2354\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">编程任务占据商用模型主要使用，但 benchmark 评估范围有限</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2357\" data-end=\"2386\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">推理任务增长迅速，但 benchmark 多偏知识问答</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"2388\" data-end=\"2391\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因此：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"2395\" data-end=\"2430\"><strong data-start=\"2395\" data-end=\"2430\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">LLM 成败不应只看 benchmark，而应看现实任务表现。</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h1 data-start=\"2437\" data-end=\"2477\"><strong data-start=\"2439\" data-end=\"2477\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">总结：AI 正进入“推理 + 工具 + 多模型 + 高度个性化”阶段</span></span></strong></h1>\n  <p data-start=\"2479\" data-end=\"2515\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">基于 100 万亿 Token 的数据，《State of AI》揭示：</span></span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2520\" data-end=\"2540\"><strong data-start=\"2520\" data-end=\"2540\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开源模型的使用量与影响力快速上升</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2544\" data-end=\"2568\"><strong data-start=\"2544\" data-end=\"2568\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Reasoning 模型成为新的主导力量</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2572\" data-end=\"2591\"><strong data-start=\"2572\" data-end=\"2591\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">角色扮演与创意任务主导开源生态</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2595\" data-end=\"2614\"><strong data-start=\"2595\" data-end=\"2614\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">代码任务与推理任务主导商用生态</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2618\" data-end=\"2654\"><strong data-start=\"2618\" data-end=\"2654\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Agentic inference（多步骤 AI 行为）正在普及</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2658\" data-end=\"2673\"><strong data-start=\"2658\" data-end=\"2673\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">多模型混合使用成为主流</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2677\" data-end=\"2702\"><strong data-start=\"2677\" data-end=\"2702\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Benchmark 已无法反映真实世界需求</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p data-start=\"2704\" data-end=\"2710\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一句话总结：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"2714\" data-end=\"2782\"><strong data-start=\"2714\" data-end=\"2782\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI 的现实使用，正在从“聊天与写作”转变为“推理 + 工程 + 代理 + 多模型工作流”。这将决定未来 AI 产品的竞争格局。</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><strong data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2074\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;fo